item.title: Sprint 0 - get my expending belly outside and exercise!
item.description:
Sprint 0 - get my expending belly outside and exercise!

Hey! My name is Carl and I'm creating AI systems at TheGrid! I'm from Quebec, Canada and mostly speak french so please forgive me for weird usage of english :) I'm always looking for some ways to push myself so I decided to start this site to share with you those experiments and see what works and what doesn't.
